<section class="program-phases">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="program-phases__title font-display">The Eight Weeks</h2>
    <div class="program-phases__timeline">

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">01</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Civic Mapping</h3>
          <p>Every board, commission, and council in your city. Know the landscape before you enter it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">02</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">How Power Actually Works</h3>
          <p>Budgets, agendas, Robert&rsquo;s Rules, public comment. The mechanics nobody teaches in school.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">03</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Policy Analysis</h3>
          <p>Read, interpret, and respond to real policy documents. If you can&rsquo;t read the language of power, you can&rsquo;t change it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">04</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Public Speaking</h3>
          <p>Three minutes of testimony can flip a vote. Make every second count.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">05</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Board Dynamics</h3>
          <p>How decisions actually get made in a room. Coalition-building, dissent, consensus.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">06</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Working the Room</h3>
          <p>Build relationships with the people already in power. Allies, mentors, people who will go to bat for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">07</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Application Strategy</h3>
          <p>Applications that stand out. Position your experience, your story, your value.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">08</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Placement</h3>
          <p>Submit applications. Nail interviews. Walk in as a participant. Walk out as a civic leader.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

